  "description": "A lone octopus in open water at 600m depth — no reef to camouflage against, no arms to anchor with. Three arms trailing upward, five pointing down into the abyss. A single slow chromatophore pulse, once every four seconds, like a lighthouse in darkness. Enormous space around a tiny alien light.",
